title: Robinhood
subTitle: A thief robs the automated teller machines of the Imperial Bank of India. Worried about the safety of the bank, the managing director decides to hire a private detective to solve the case.

title: Kadha, Samvidhanam Kunchakko
subTitle: Kunchacko, a millionaire who built his fortune through questionable means, marries Mary and vows to change. However, leaving his past behind proves to be harder than he imagined.

title: Al Mallu
subTitle: After being cheated on by her prospective groom, Nayana learns that he also cheated on one of her close friends too. Thus, she decides to teach him a lesson.

title: God's Own Country
subTitle: The lives of a taxi driver, a man travelling to Kerala and a public prosecutor intertwine with each other as they seek monetary aid and justice.

title: Ring Master
subTitle: Prince, a dog trainer, faces an awkward situation when his pet dog Diana acts in a film alongside his former lover, an actress who shares the same name as the dog.

title: Vishwaroopam 2
subTitle: Wisam Ahmad Kashmiri, a RAW agent, tries to prevent a terrorist organisation from executing a deadly mission against three countries.

title: Aadu 2
subTitle: Shaji Pappan and his team participate in a tug-of-war tournament to overcome their financial crisis. However, fate entangles them in a counterfeiting deal.

title: Kammatti Paadam
subTitle: Krishnan returns home to Kammattippaadam after a call from his friend Ganga. Together, they face their dark past as old crimes resurface, putting their lives in danger.

title: King of Kotha
subTitle: Heartbroken on being back-stabbed by his childhood friend, Raju, an influential man, runs away from his hometown, Kotha. Soon, to bring back order in the town, a police officer plots a plan.

title: Vikrithi
subTitle: After spending two sleepless nights taking care of his sick daughter, a person with hearing and speech disability falls asleep in a metro. A passenger photographs him and shares it online.

title: Vikrithi
subTitle: After spending two sleepless nights taking care of his sick daughter, a person with hearing and speech disability falls asleep in a metro. A passenger photographs him and shares it online.

title: Money Ratnam
subTitle: Neil, a showroom executive, finds a bag full of money after a party. Later, he receives a call to meet at a secluded spot where he finds four strangers and gets involved in a dangerous deal.

title: Manoharam
subTitle: Manu, a talented poster artist, struggles to find work with the advent of digital technology. After being jilted by his fiancee, he attempts to rebuild his life.

title: Minnaminnikkoottam
subTitle: Ajit, an anchor in Kolkata, meets Krishnapriya, who has lost her husband under mysterious circumstances. However, things become complicated when he falls for her while helping to find her spouse.

title: Srungaravelan
subTitle: Kanan falls in love with Raddhu, the daughter of a ruthless city gangster responsible for numerous deaths. To marry her, Kanan must confront the dangers and challenges that lie ahead.

title: Take Off
subTitle: Sameera, an Indian nurse working in Iraq, and her colleagues are held hostage by terrorists. Later, Indian ambassador Manoj uses his wit to rescue them and get them out of the country alive.

title: Lucifer
subTitle: The demise of the leader of a political party leads to a massive power struggle. Amidst the chaos, a mystical man named Stephen comes in to ascend the throne.

title: 12th Fail
subTitle: After a cheating attempt comes to light, Manoj Kumar Sharma, fails his tests. Years later, determined to become a police officer, Manoj attempts one of the most difficult exams in the country.

title: Bromance
subTitle: When Binto learns of his brother Shinto's disappearance, his search for Shinto leads him to collaborate with others, resulting in unforeseen turns, revelations, and memorable experiences.

title: Salaar
subTitle: Just when the prince of Khansaar is about to rise to the throne, a plan of overthrowing him is exercised and only one man can help him retrieve power.

title: Salaar

title: Utharaswayamvaram
subTitle: After facing numerous struggles, Prakashan finally marries his dream girl, Uthara. However, their marriage lasts less than a day, leading to a major clash between their families.

title: Dhamaka
subTitle: Things get complicated when Swami and Anand, two look-alike men from different backgrounds, fall in love with the same girl.

title: Cheriya Kallanum Valiya Poleesum
subTitle: Sadasivan comes across a house where the owner, Kumaran, has committed suicide to protect his wife, Soumini. However, what is even stranger is that a man who is visually challenged is always around.

title: Honey Bee
subTitle: A man proposes to his close friend on the night before her wedding. However, he incurs the wrath of her older brothers when he elopes with her.

title: Naran
subTitle: Velayudhan, an orphan, is loved by the villagers as he keeps the village free from unsavoury people and practices. However, an evil moneylender and politician get jealous and try to get rid of him.

title: Thrissur Pooram
subTitle: Pullu Giri is trying to live a peaceful life and forget his ruffian past. Following an incident, he gets dragged into the affairs of some local gangs.

title: Malikappuram
subTitle: A young aspiring film director who seeks to make his directorial debut decides to use a real-life gangster as inspiration for his first movie.

title: Kuberaa
subTitle: Following a tycoon's discovery of a rare oil reserve, a compassionate beggar gets trapped in the dangerous mechanisms of his rapacious scheme.

title: Classmates
subTitle: A group of college friends meet after many years for a class reunion. However, due to some unexpected turn of events, several dark secrets are revealed, which changes their lives.
